Field Description
Authorization

Basic Access Authentication token.
Accept optional

application/json, application/xml, text/yaml, text/plain.

card – Relevant for Create “action”
  action String

update/delete/get
  parameters Object
    description String

Alphanumeric field (e.g. (ASI Port 1, etc)
    port Number

    general Object

Section for Mandatory General fields
      enable Boolean

false (D) / true
      direction String

In (D) / Out
      inSettings Object

          mode String

Based on PCR (D) / Based on Bitrate
          latency Number

Numeric field
        externalStatmux Number

Boolean

(Mbps) Numeric field
        outputPacketSize String

188 (D) / 204

false (D) / true
        shutdownStabilization Numeric

Numeric field

Numeric field

Numeric field
        mirrorTs Object

Applicable for Mirror TS
          mirrorsIdsList String[]

Read-only List of destinations (“Physical object Ids”) of the Mirrors TS(s)

String field which will be used to link to the Master Socket object

https://<IP Address>/restapi/v4/active-alarms

Header

Field Description
Authorization

Basic Access Authentication token.
Accept optional

application/json, application/xml, text/yaml, text/plain.

Default value: application/json

Parameter

Field Type Description
severity Boolean

true for severity field in result
recovery Boolean

true for recoveryTip field in result
  • Request Examples - url 
[ip]/restapi/v4/active-alarms
[ip]/restapi/v4/active-alarms?severity=true
[ip]/restapi/v4/active-alarms?recovery=true
[ip]/restapi/v4/active-alarms?severity=true&recovery=true

Success 200

Field Type Description
tag String
assertTime String
objectId String
description String
severity String

optional by query (e.g. restapi/v4/active-alarms?severity=true)
recoveryTip String

optional by query (e.g. restapi/v4/active-alarms?recovery=true)

Header

Field Description
Authorization

Basic Access Authentication token.
Accept optional

application/json, application/xml, text/yaml, text/plain.

Default value: application/json

Parameter

Field Type Description
  id String

Unique String field - Relevant for update/get “action”
  tag String

card
  action String

update/get
  parameters Object
    cardType String

Main, Iom, Quad10G, Dual10G, OctalASI, None (D) - (applicable for PCIe cards only)

Alphanumeric field
    serialNumber String

Alphanumeric field

Alphanumeric field
    portRedundancy1 Object
      mode String

Note: Teaming redundancy mode is service affecting as application restarts

Allowed values: "Off", "Hot-Standby", "Dual", "Teaming"

      scheme String

Applicable when Mode: Hot-Standby

Allowed values: "Manual", "Manual Revert", "Automatic", "Automatic Revert"

      activePort String

Applicable when Scheme: Manual

Allowed values: "Primary", "Backup"

    portRedundancy2 Object

Allowed values: "Off", "Hot-Standby", "Dual", "Teaming"

      scheme String

Allowed values: "Manual", "Manual Revert", "Automatic", "Automatic Revert"

      activePort String

Allowed values: "Primary", "Backup"
